<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss house</title><updated>2025-12-05T04:35:56.597441+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=110&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>0ba02ec25e23eaabd27fba6f4f2a1e5b</id><title>移民絕對是正確的選擇</title><updated>2025-12-04T18:13:21+08:00</updated><author><name>hkduck123</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-04T18:13:21+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574916986"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574916986"&gt;唔好問點解，自己找答案&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100274&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-04T18:13:21+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>43112de2916d173bddd9a5b195aa42dd</id><title>專家樓評：網紅成功申請按揭有竅妙</title><updated>2025-12-04T18:16:00+08:00</updated><author><name>Enner</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-04T18:16:00+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574917018"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574917018"&gt;早前有旅遊界網紅豪擲逾億元購入北角一手特色戶，成為城中熱話。事實上，近年網上愈來愈多人投身成為網紅，其中不少著名網紅的吸金能力相當強勁，成功置業亦不再是難事。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他們通常不會固定受薪於單一職業，多半身兼數職，追求工作多樣化與彈性，因此可視為斜槓族(Slasher)。然而，當他們置業並申請按揭貸款時，由於缺乏穩定收入及正式的收入證明，銀行通常較難評估還款能力。是次將針對此類人士，解析如何更容易獲得銀行按揭批核的方法。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;固定收入人士在申請按揭時，只需提供最近3個月銀行入息證明、強積金紀錄及一年的稅單。然而，網紅普遍屬於自僱人士，收入較不穩定，因此銀行所需的證明文件較多，包括最近6個月的入息證明，以及最近一至兩個課稅年度的稅單等。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;定時入帳 保留半年紀錄&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;若他們以現金或支票方式領取薪金，建議養成每月定時...&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="574917018" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_251204/20251204_24441db483fd323059b1iU16qJS10yDy.jpeg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_251204/20251204_24441db483fd323059b1iU16qJS10yDy.jpeg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/9d2658/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_251204/20251204_24441db483fd323059b1iU16qJS10yDy.jpeg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;首先你要係一個網紅 仲要有幾十萬個粉&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;新聞來源連結: &lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20251204%2Fbkn-20251204070007761-1204_00842_001.html&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=ff875a5c3970327c654baef5e3c48c4c&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank" uhash="ff875a5c3970327c654baef5e3c48c4c"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20251204/bkn-20251204070007761-1204_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100279&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-04T18:16:00+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a59c0d0e4bdea5657f2d3fe2fd59513b</id><title>馬雲話：未來嘅房子會愈嚟愈唔值錢，房價如蔥。</title><updated>2025-12-04T19:09:12+08:00</updated><author><name>Nebraska</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-04T19:09:12+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574917568"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574917568"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/f7fOwfiNzMk?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/f7fOwfiNzMk?si=06OMRIEbcxcOAq2_" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/f7fOwfiNzMk?si=06OMRIEbcxcOAq2_&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;馬雲（Jack Ma）喺2017年左右嘅一次演講或者訪問入面，的確講過類似嘅說法。佢話：「未來嘅房子會愈嚟愈唔值錢，房價如蔥。」意思就係未來房價會好似蔥咁平，唔會再貴落去，只會愈嚟愈低。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;呢個預言喺當時引起好大迴響，好多人覺得佢太激進，但而家睇落嚟，中國樓市真係有啲趨勢朝住呢個方向走，尤其係三四線城市同埋人口流出嘅地方，房價已經開始回落。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;當然，一線城市如北京、上海嘅核心地段，可能仲會維持相對穩定，但整體嚟講，馬雲嘅觀點係基於科技進步、城市化放緩同埋人口結構變化，預測住宅需求會減少，供應會增加。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 Nebraska 於 2025-12-4 19:12 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100310&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-04T19:09:12+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>bc18ee812b2ce82f7430ca699bf5021b</id><title>近排租務市場咁旺 嚟緊年尾 各位業主打算加幾多租</title><updated>2025-12-04T20:33:29+08:00</updated><author><name>羊腩煲好好味</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-04T20:33:29+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574918458"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574918458"&gt;我加住兩成先啦&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="23" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/victory.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100356&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-04T20:33:29+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>7a518e321c94c88c2637ab9a97f085cb</id><title>屯門怡樂花園要急拆棚網，業主又要用一大筆錢</title><updated>2025-12-04T20:41:42+08:00</updated><author><name>冗員七號</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-04T20:41:42+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574918538"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574918538"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16662548" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="574918538" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_251204/20251204_f670cfc44a2323ffeb1bhSeVQoARV0jq.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/e7b3aa/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_251204/20251204_f670cfc44a2323ffeb1bhSeVQoARV0jq.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16662548_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16662548&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20251204_203701_815.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (82.46 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-12-4 20:41&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;業主真係陰功囉，就算供完，又要俾32至220萬的錢拆網，如果諗得太耐燒著了，咁就大鑊&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100363&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-04T20:41:42+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>7f71d17c72c472b5f9d20363d3ca7dea</id><title>我估之后過年會取消放煙花</title><updated>2025-12-05T01:59:38+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin166688</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-05T01:59:38+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574921052"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574921052"&gt;&lt;div class="videoContainer" style="width:640px;height:360px"&gt;&lt;div class="videocontent"&gt;&lt;video class="contentElement" controls="" controlslist="nodownload" id="contentElement_21167e5b5145403704258056650" poster="https://1253590913.vod2.myqcloud.com/743b5de7vodhk1253590913/21167e5b5145403704258056650/5145403704258059323.jpg" preload="none"&gt;&lt;source src="https://1253590913.vod2.myqcloud.com/4b254b8fvodtranshk1253590913/21167e5b5145403704258056650/v.f100030.mp4"/&gt;&lt;/video&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="adContainer" id="adContainer_21167e5b5145403704258056650"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="coverContainer" id="coverContainer_21167e5b5145403704258056650" onclick="requestAds('21167e5b5145403704258056650');" style="display:none;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;今年十月一中國國慶大埔廣福宏福對出海放所謂煙花&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100583&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-05T01:59:38+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a0fcf987b106975a2beda666d8666936</id><title>名人沽貨丨著名監製梅小青906萬售浪澄灣兩房</title><updated>2025-12-05T10:13:47+08:00</updated><author><name>好久冇見</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-05T10:13:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574923413"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574923413"&gt;【信報財經新聞】無綫電視前監製梅小青售出大角咀浪澄灣一個2房單位，作價906.8萬元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;市場消息指出，上述售出的單位為8座中低層C室，實用面積549方呎，2房間隔，座向東方，可享開揚都市景，連同租約以906.8萬元沽出，實用呎價16517元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原業主於2012年以686萬元買入單位，持貨已經13年，是次沽出單位賬面獲利220.8萬元，期內升值32%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據悉，原業主為著名電視監製梅小青，曾經負責「原振俠」、「法證先鋒」系列及「宮心計」系列等劇集。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D951298&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=504367c0df9f5c3e726b88518d42f83e&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank" uhash="504367c0df9f5c3e726b88518d42f83e"&gt;https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=951298&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100765&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-05T10:13:47+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>7c76fd6aeba3402bee2127bd14e5e3b2</id><title>未到聖𧩙工商舖物業已經開始Free Fall</title><updated>2025-12-05T10:21:37+08:00</updated><author><name>okla3</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-05T10:21:37+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574923488"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574923488"&gt;麥當勞黃金租約都要7厘幾先沽得出，全海景甲級寫字樓平到萬八蚊尺才有人接貨，開始人踩人慘劇發生！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32100772&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=18236406986932612cba1784_05832419"/><published>2025-12-05T10:21:37+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>bd64819a646fe33b25574600523951ac</id><title>創興港元定存3個月年利率3.1厘</title><updated>2025-12-05T10:33:17+08:00</updated><author><name>驚青猛男</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-12-05T10:33:17+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574923603"&gt;&lt;!